  "text": "The design of new gestures is a major challenge. The gestures have to be simple, easy to learn and quick to write. This holds for the set presented in this paper, but with a growing number of gestures, their complexity might rise significantly, which could complicate their use. It might be beneficial to explore multiple combinations of gestures and patterns [CITATION_1] [18] of their use.",
